<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" style="font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Contribution Confirmation - Raizefund</title>
</head>

<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #ffffff;">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #ffffff; padding: 40px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table width="480" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 8px;">
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 24px 40px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
              <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">Raizefund</h1>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 32px 40px; color: #000000;">
              <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px;">Dear Supporter,</p>

              <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 24px;">
                Thank you for your generous contribution to the campaign <strong>"{{campaignTitle}}"</strong> on
                Raizefund!
              </p>

              <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                Your anonymous donation of <strong>{{currency}}{{contributionAmount}}</strong> is a meaningful step
                toward helping the campaign achieve its goals. While we cannot reveal your identity, your support will
                be felt by the campaign creator and those they aim to help.
              </p>

              <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 28px;">
                Your contribution is now on its way to making a difference. Thank you for being a part of something
                bigger!
              </p>

              <div style="text-align: center; margin: 24px 0;">
                <a href="{{campaignUrl}}"
                  style="display: inline-block; text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid #000000; color: #000000; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 14px;">
                  View the Campaign
                </a>
              </div>

              <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #333333; margin-bottom: 0;">
                With sincere thanks,<br />
                <strong>The Raizefund Team</strong>
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td
              style="padding: 14px 0; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666666; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
              Â© {{year}} Raizefund. All rights reserved.
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>

</html>